Date: Tue, 11 Dec 2012 17:34:27 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 013/518] t4240: update T4 PCIE controller interrupts dts node

For platform T4240, internal interrupts 4-7 are assigned as PCIE0-4
interrupts. This patch updates dts to meet PCIE hardware.

Signed-off-by: Minghuan Lian <Minghuan.Lian@freescale.com>
Signed-off-by: Andy Fleming <afleming@freescale.com>
[Grabbed from the branch, LINUX_IR5.2.0, of
https://git.freescale.com/git-private/cgit.cgi/ppc/alu-b4860/linux.git.]
Signed-off-by: Tiejun Chen <tiejun.chen@windriver.com>
---
 arch/powerpc/boot/dts/fsl/t4240si-post.dtsi |   16 ++++++++--------
 1 files changed, 8 insertions(+), 8 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/powerpc/boot/dts/fsl/t4240si-post.dtsi b/arch/powerpc/boot/dts/fsl/t4240si-post.dtsi
index 3719040..e1d2451 100644
--- a/arch/powerpc/boot/dts/fsl/t4240si-post.dtsi
+++ b/arch/powerpc/boot/dts/fsl/t4240si-post.dtsi
@@ -59,13 +59,13 @@
 	#address-cells = <3>;
 	bus-range = <0x0 0xff>;
 	clock-frequency = <33333333>;
-	interrupts = <16 2 1 15>;
+	interrupts = <20 2 0 0>;
 	pcie@0 {
 		#interrupt-cells = <1>;
 		#size-cells = <2>;
 		#address-cells = <3>;
 		device_type = "pci";
-		interrupts = <16 2 1 15>;
+		interrupts = <20 2 0 0>;
 		interrupt-map-mask = <0xf800 0 0 7>;
 		interrupt-map = <
 			/* IDSEL 0x0 */
@@ -85,13 +85,13 @@
 	#address-cells = <3>;
 	bus-range = <0 0xff>;
 	clock-frequency = <33333333>;
-	interrupts = <16 2 1 14>;
+	interrupts = <21 2 0 0>;
